dct_title_s: Map of the central portion of the Upper Peninsula, Michigan.
dct_description_sm: With legend. Julius Bien, lithographer. Copy 2 has manuscript red coloring annotated to show iron ore deposits. "Pl.II." from the Atlas accompanying reports on Upper Peninsula of Michigan 1869-1873. 1 map; 85 x 69 cm
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
